{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6547: Combine component and slot to realize transparent transmission of class, style and attrs to a certain slot",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:40.702747+00:00",
  "text": "Combine component and slot to realize transparent transmission of class, style and attrs to a certain slot\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\n\r\nCombine component and slot to realize transparent transmission of class, style and attrs to a certain slot\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\n\r\n```html\r\n/* Define */\r\n/* grid-view.vue */\r\n<script setup>\r\ndefineProps({\r\n  col: {\r\n    type: Number,\r\n    default: 2,\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n</script>\r\n<template>\r\n<component\r\n    :is=\"$slots.default\"\r\n    :style=\"`grid-template-columns: repeat(${col}, 1fr);`\"\r\n    aaa=\"bbb\"\r\n    class=\"grid-view\">\r\n</component>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n/* Usage */\r\n/* page.vue */\r\n<template>\r\n<grid-view>\r\n    <el-form></el-form>\r\n</grid-view>\r\n</template>\r\n```\r\nIn essence, slot can be regarded as a function component. It is hoped that class, style and attrs can be transparently transmitted to the el-form component in this way to change the style of the el-form component.",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request"
  ],
